{"tid":2396110,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生旺角衝突藏雷射筆罪成還押候判 警方替被告快速搜身時找不到涉案雷射筆","createTime":"2021-02-05T10:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T13:25:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb3a5d2011f32fcd2d5c9319b9a1b7381cc4e7d","tid":2396110,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13479&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=69e7ceb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13479</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第七庭 <br />\n#梁嘉琪裁判官 <br />\n#1027旺角 <br />\n#裁決<br />\n#攻擊性武器 #雷射筆<br />\n<br />\n👤陳(17) <br />\n<br />\n控罪<br />\n(1)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n被控於2019年10月27日，在旺角道及彌敦道交界，管有一支發出鐳射光束的工具。 <br />\n<br />\n‼️罪名成立‼️<br />\n押後至2月19日1200九龍城裁判法院第六庭判刑，索取勞教中心及更生中心報告，期間還押‼️<br />\n<br />\n(手足進犯人欄前向旁聽席飛吻😭)<br />\n<br />\n(裁決理由後補)"},{"pid":"8804a0d5342ee0d63e1bab9cd9418a9982564682","tid":2396110,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"18歲學生在前年10年旺角衝突中，遭警方制服後搜出一枝3B級雷射筆，被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪。他早前受審，今在九龍城裁判法院被裁定罪名成立，並須還押至本月19日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n辯方在審訊時，爭議證物鏈的完整性及被告並無犯案意圖。然而梁嘉琪裁判官今裁決指，雖然警方替被告快速搜身時，在他身上找不到涉案雷射筆，但由於當時警員的關注點是利器，加上雷射筆只得3吋長，故當時未有搜出亦可以理解。<br />\n<br />\n梁官又認為，即使警員的紀錄不完整，亦不代表證物鏈斷裂。反而被告被捕後一直抱住自己的背囊，他一定知道內有涉案雷射筆。而根據他當日的裝束、裝備及環境環境，可推斷他必然知道會有衝突發生，並打算用涉案雷射筆傷人。"},{"pid":"d992ae285f2cdb185287e3e4f039679e1cf44a3c","tid":2396110,"uid":64103,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:35:37.000Z","msg":"痴X線<br />\n就快可以用虛構故事作為證供<br />\n唔需要任何實質嘅證據"},{"pid":"f35ab8c917dd8e76320a0211eda8f5fb5930a151","tid":2396110,"uid":161935,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"先唔講雷射筆點解會犯法。<br />\n<br />\n而家你都搜唔到有武器，然後話你總之一定有武器，然後重判，只會逼人真係拎武器，因為反正守規矩都會被人屈入去坐嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過香港人忍耐力極限係超越世界第二好多倍，所以到而家仲未有咩法官被襲。777都預見到，禁埋香港人起底，透過家人去攻擊啲納粹法庭劊子手。"},{"pid":"6925956ed27e059e86b0ad4944631fd90c9ddc67","tid":2396110,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"其實法律上<br />\n係咪真係點都冇得打?"},{"pid":"c8475df9b37f857a33b39a7c53a6036618936aa6","tid":2396110,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"打算用鐳射筆傷人？？？<br />\n又推論？？<br />\n冇証物都推到入罪？？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e622b50dd3c979caba8fe4aafead2466f5c3af9","tid":2396110,"uid":34811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6925956ed27e059e86b0ad4944631fd90c9ddc67","tid":2396110,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"其實法律上<br />\n係咪真係點都冇得打?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"高院幫手寫咗唔少故仔俾紅官用<br />\n通常都係用陳耀成案同SHY案<br />\n附近有抗爭就容許無限推論<br />\n有啲會打舊電池，但係李運強bam咗呢個打法"},{"pid":"0b0846016c4826ed4ec8fc791af433fdd6ed7f38","tid":2396110,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"獲准匿名的警長 X 在審訊時供稱，他向被告背部連開 5 發胡椒球槍欲截停，稱一發射擊不足以截停一個人，但承認訓練未試過向人體發射，故不確定胡椒球彈的實際威力。<span class=\"red\">他又指案發現場無衝突，亦無人使用過鐳射筆。</span><br />\n<br />\n梁都幾弱智, 咁情況就唔止傷人可能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前幾單入到係因為附近有人用黎照狗, <br />\n而家好明顯冇都得一個推論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809375c5fbe053b4226789d7e45f8cc919d784c5","tid":2396110,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-27-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%A3%E9%96%8B-5-%E7%99%BC%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E7%90%83%E6%A7%8D%E6%88%AA%E5%81%9C-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%97%8F%E9%90%B3%E5%B0%84%E7%AD%86%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E6%80%9D%E8%A6%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%AA%BF%E6%AF%8D%E6%8A%B1%E9%A0%AD%E7%97%9B%E5%93%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-27-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%2596%258B-5-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%2581%259C-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E6%2580%259D%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%258A%25B1%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2597%259B%25E5%2593%25AD%2F&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjPUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=2bf12b15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-27-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%2596%258B-5-%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%2581%259C-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%2590%25B3%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E6%2580%259D%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E5%25